{"title":"山坡羊（曲三首）","authors":["马凯"],"dates":[{"year":2003,"month":9,"day":11}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"山坡羊（曲三首）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"马凯"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红日"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拔白破夜，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"吐红化雪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"云开雾散春晖泻。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"煦相接，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"绿相偕，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"东来紫气盈川岳。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"最是光明洒无界，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"升，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也烨烨；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"落，也烨烨。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"明月"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"星空银厦，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"粼波倒塔，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小桥倩影谁描画？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"皓无瑕，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"素无华，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"悄悄来去静无价。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只把清辉留天下，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"无牵挂；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"去，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"无牵挂。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"自在人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"胸中有海，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"眼底无碍，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呼吁宇宙通天脉。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"伴春来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"润花开，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只为山河添新彩。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"试问安能常自在？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"名，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也身外，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"利，也身外。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":15,"page_end":15}